                  "id": "Yzgzk",
                  "name": "prodDescText",
                  "fill": "#475658",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "This special edition of the Kamaleon Jacket is a tribute to circular design. By combining the classic silhouette of our favorite cropped denim jacket with the application of our recycled fibers, a new functional everyday classic has been reborn. Made in Guatemala City, in partnership with The New Denim Project, this jacket is made from 100% upcycled denim fibers, diverting textile waste from landfills and breathing new life into what would have otherwise been cotton scraps.",
